        <h3 class="title">One Day Pass</h3>
        <p>Explore Kuwalt's rich history on an all-inclusive tour of Al Salam Palace Museum. Our expert guides will take you on a journey through the palace's story and the history of the land. It's the perfect way to experience Kuwait's past.</p>
